The paper deals with the problem of inferring additional facts from a knowledge base, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of external information such as relation schemas and entity taxonomies suggests a focus on natural language processing (cs.CL) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the application of the method to question answering, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
